metadata.title: Bush Business Furniture Move 60 Series Height Adjustable Standing Desk, 72W x 30D, Platinum Gray with Cool Gray Metallic Base
features: Height adjustable motorized base paired with top surface
Durable thermally fused laminate work surface features superior resistance to scratches and stains
Two stage units provide height range from 27 to 46.7 inches high and operates at speed of 0.78 inches per second
Four programmable presets with a quiet, soft-touch start and stop
Quiet UL listed electric motors; 10 foot power cord plugs into standard wall outlet
description: Have a healthy and productive day at the office with the Move 60 Series by Bush Business Furniture 72W x 30D Height Adjustable Standing Desk. Those who use sit to stand desks report improved attitudes, energy and comfort while getting more done, and the Move 60 Series provides an affordable solution. Sit and stand throughout your day without missing a beat in your home office or at work. The electric adjustable height Desk includes a 10 foot power cord and smoothly lifts from a low of 27 inches to a high of 46.7 at the push of a button. Store your favorite heights with four programmable presets so you can use them as often as you like. The ergonomic Desk withstands years of everyday use. A durable thermally fused laminate finish resists scratches and stains, while the sturdy steel base creates a weight capacity of up to 200 pounds. This sit to stand Desk will have no problem holding all of your work materials. Backed by a 5 Year Warranty, the Height Adjustable Standing Desk meets ANSI/BIFMA quality test standards for safety and performance. A variety of finishes and sizes fit home offices, large multi-person workspaces or anywhere in between. Find the right height for you with Move 60.
